# AIVibe Core

- Use `AGENTS.md` as the root contract.
- Use `commands/` as the stage entry layer.
- Use `skills/` as the executable workflow layer.
- Prefer `/spec -> /plan -> /build -> /test -> /review -> /ship`.
- Do not skip directly to implementation if the stage is still unclear.
